{
  "stem": "734.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and carefully, you know, watched and all that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is-- this is what my job was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At the same time, Kurt was the most generous individual you could have imagined.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because the kapos always had the worst rep-- reputation in camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were some beasts among them, no question about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And how this man never got-- I mean, how this man could stay human as he was in camp is beyond me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I could never stand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was just a-- [SIGHS] The biggest heart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Just a-- an amazing individual.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He-- when he found out-- first-- first of all, he would bring food, extra food, whatever he could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because he realized that to exist on this food was impossible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He would always throw in some bread, an apple, whatever he could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "One day he found out that I have a sister and two aunts working.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That is, in Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He found out-- I know-- at that time, I already knew where they were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were working on the same field where I lived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They lived on a different field.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But they worked on the same field where I lived, in a barrack, where they did weave artillery baskets.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They weaved the baskets for artillery shells, my sister and two aunts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But we never had a chance to contact each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because when they came-- came in, in the morning, I would be on my way out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Therefore, we never saw each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every once in a blue moon, she would wave from far away, while I was leaving, marching out to another field where we had our workplace, right?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as soon as he found out that [?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
